Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Besides this recently reported event, Russia also reported 2 events of LSD, in May 2016 and in June 2017. The situation for each of these LSD events is as follows:

1. Event May 2016, started on 25 May 2016, 313 outbreaks were reported. The event was resolved on [Wed 15 Feb 2017]. See event summary and updated map: http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=20252

2. Event June 2017, started on [Mon 5 Jun 2017], 42 outbreaks were reported. The event was resolved on [Fri 17 Nov 2017]. See event summary and updated map: http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=24049.

